tables.table_schema:
CREATE TABLE AR_VR_Analytics (
    session_id UUID,
    user_id INT,
    event_type VARCHAR(50),
    event_time TIMESTAMP,
    event_data JSONB
);

CREATE TABLE AR_VR_Sessions (
    session_id INT PRIMARY KEY,
    user_id INT,
    session_duration INT,
    session_date TIMESTAMP,
    FOREIGN KEY (user_id) REFERENCES AR_VR_Users(user_id)
);

CREATE TABLE AR_VR_Performance (
    performance_id INT PRIMARY KEY,
    session_id INT,
    render_time FLOAT,
    frame_rate FLOAT,
    memory_usage INT,
    FOREIGN KEY (session_id) REFERENCES AR_VR_Sessions(session_id)
);

CREATE TABLE AR_VR_Users (
    user_id INT PRIMARY KEY,
    username VARCHAR(50),
    age INT,
    gender VARCHAR(10),
    location VARCHAR(100)
)

CREATE TABLE AR_VR_Events (
    event_id INT PRIMARY KEY,
    user_id INT,
    event_type VARCHAR(50),
    event_timestamp TIMESTAMP,
    event_data JSON
)

CREATE TABLE AR_VR_Performance (
    performance_id INT PRIMARY KEY,
    user_id INT,
    session_id INT,
    performance_metric VARCHAR(50),
    performance_value FLOAT
)

CREATE TABLE AR_VR_Analytics (
    analytics_id INT PRIMARY KEY,
    user_id INT,
    event_id INT,
    analytics_data JSON
)

CREATE TABLE AR_VR_Sessions (
  session_id UUID PRIMARY KEY,
  user_id UUID NOT NULL,
  session_start TIMESTAMP NOT NULL,
  session_end TIMESTAMP NOT NULL,
  session_duration INTERVAL NOT NULL
)

CREATE TABLE AR_VR_Events (
  event_id UUID PRIMARY KEY,
  session_id UUID NOT NULL,
  event_type VARCHAR(50) NOT NULL,
  event_timestamp TIMESTAMP NOT NULL
)

CREATE TABLE AR_VR_Users (
  user_id UUID PRIMARY KEY,
  user_name VARCHAR(100) NOT NULL,
  user_age INT,
  user_gender VARCHAR(10)
)

CREATE TABLE AR_VR_Performance (
  performance_id UUID PRIMARY KEY,
  session_id UUID NOT NULL,
  fps_avg FLOAT,
  cpu_usage FLOAT,
  gpu_usage FLOAT
)

CREATE TABLE AR_VR_Usage (
  usage_id UUID PRIMARY KEY,
  session_id UUID NOT NULL,
  user_id UUID NOT NULL,
  usage_duration INTERVAL NOT NULL
)
